title: The Strong, The Few, True Cultivators on Campus
description: The Strong, The Few, True Cultivators on Campus ManhuaTang Zheng found his world turned horribly upside down when he lost his greatness after an incident. He meets Tian Chanzi in the haunted basement, and he learns he was born with a Nine Yang Saint Body. An exciting series following Tang Zheng’s misadventures as he tries to master his newfound abilities. 同学，你真行！
